Class FileRequestHandler

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.github.pulsebeat02.minecraftmedialibrary.http.FileRequestHandler
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ClientRequest, FileRequest, RequestHandler, java.lang.Runnable

    public class FileRequestHandler
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Runnable, FileRequest
    A class used to handle incoming requests. It checks if the current request being received is a GET request and sends the correct response back to the client.
